{
  "chapter": 228,
  "chapter_summary": "婠婠与寇仲、徐子陵在城中酒桌谈判，要求在杨公宝库中先取一件东西以换取暂时议和。寇仲与婠婠勾指为誓，达成协议。婠婠以勾指之名施展天魔劲震慑米放，揭示其知晓米放狼王身份。契丹马贼首领窟哥率百余骑入城，婠婠声称与己无关，飘然离去。寇仲与徐子陵独面百余契丹马贼，陈家风等人在城门埋伏断敌退路。婠婠以丝带开路杀出城门，寇仲以井中月、徐子陵以劈空掌大战群寇。米放以狼牙棒攻击徐子陵，被螺旋劲震飞。寇仲截击米放于半空，战况惨烈，长街血流成河。寇仲嘲讽窟哥癞虾蟆想吃天鹅肉，窟哥始觉大势已去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只要你们肯答应让我们在'杨公宝库'内先取其中一件东西，我们便可暂时议和，息止干戈。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "究竟是甚么东西那么重要，可否清楚说出，那我们便可作出考虑。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "可能是个盒子，也可能是个小箱，但绝对和财富兵器没有关系，至于里面是甚么东西，请恕奴家要卖个关子，总言之你们得到它亦没有用处。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "不要用这种眼光表情款待小弟好吗？惹得小弟误会了便不太好，因为小弟一向都爱自作多情的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这交易似对我们没有甚么损害，纵使深仇大恨，也可等起出'杨公宝库'后才计较。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你爱怎样就怎样吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "那就此一言为定，但假若你食言妄动干戈，此事便拉倒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那就让我们勾指作实，反悔者将不得好死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "不是又有甚么阴谋诡计吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "没胆鬼！枉我还当你是能令人家倾心的男人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇郎啊！你莫要反悔呀！否则奴家绝不会放过你的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ku_ge",
      "text": "兀那汉子，是否就是来自契丹的窟哥？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_ge",
      "speaker_name": "窟哥",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "既知我窟哥之名，还敢坐在这里卿卿我我，风花雪月，是否活得不耐烦。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ku_ge",
      "text": "老兄你说得好，我们既知你是何方神圣，却又敢坐在这里饮酒作乐，恭候大驾，自然不是因活得不耐烦哩！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只是个过路的客人，你们要打生打死，一概与我无关，奴家要走了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_ge",
      "speaker_name": "窟哥",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "请问美人儿欲要到那里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_mi_fang",
      "text": "这位前辈该就是横行东北，有'狼王'之称的米放米老师吧？近来绝迹中原，想不到竟是投靠了契丹人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mi_fang",
      "speaker_name": "米放",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "你是何派何人弟子，竟知道米某人来历。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_mi_fang",
      "text": "米老儿你坐稳，这位大小姐的师尊就是…嘿！对不起！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这才是听话的孩子嘛！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "小姐你不是要走吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "请顺手关上城门！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_ge",
      "speaker_name": "窟哥",
      "listener": "char_wan_wan",
      "text": "美人儿想走吗？没那么容易吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_ge",
      "speaker_name": "窟哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀了他们！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_wan",
      "speaker_name": "婠婠",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "关中再见吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "她怎知'杨公宝库'是在关中的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我又不是她肚子内的蛔虫，怎会知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们为受害同胞取回血债的时候到了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "痛快！痛快！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ku_ge",
      "text": "哥老兄的美人儿溜了吗？癞虾蟆岂非吃不到天鹅肉。这么深奥的一句你明白吗？要不要我说得浅易些。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲少！这老家伙是你的！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_ge",
      "speaker_name": "窟哥",
      "listener": "char_mi_fang",
      "text": "米公小心",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 228,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    }
  ],
